title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Jamie Foxx Can't Get In
description: Ryan Reynolds was called rude publicly by a co-star, so Ryan reached out privately to fix the situation… Ryan’s co-star felt the need to share that publicly as well. And Jamie Foxx was rejected at the door while trying to get into Cardi B’s birthday party.
